title: #268 Quiet Turd
description:
Hot tamale, it's a trippy Tuesdays folks, as Joe hates Robert Redford and tours the Southwest with Sal Vulcano while Mark does a hot weekend at Gotham Comedy Club before taking shrooms at The National concert with the gal. Check it out!
